ime":"2018-02-09T03:04:49.000Z","msg":"青少年軍好似係梁太搞的..<br />\n啲「非牟利團體」好多野玩..."},{"pid":"824eefbda94c02ef73d1966c4e3ec512604fa369","tid":554794,"uid":44358,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e3b8eb6156f7453cd4e042ed28659f073ea607c7","tid":554794,"uid":29423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:04:49.000Z","msg":"青少年軍好似係梁太搞的..<br />\n啲「非牟利團體」好多野玩..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:36:51.000Z","msg":"乜野叫青少年軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我只知龍蝦兵團。<br />\n<br />\n邊撚個梁太？？<br />\n人形龍蝦我就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4a5e3c033863c3668ac2a5550d192d05fbb964","tid":554794,"uid":15503,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:39:25.000Z","msg":"中式步操傷膝頭，而且難過英式步操好多<br />\n上面啲制服團隊好多都唔係Full Time<br />\n一個月返得嗰兩三日<br />\n邊個肯同你練呀<br />\n<br />\n仲有一班就退休有柴頭嘅廢中<br />\n英式步操都Hea你<br />\n要中式步操佢一定直頭唔撚操啦"},{"pid":"a02a47e7b7cc7598cf085ade17cdc3a30c5372ce","tid":554794,"uid":4519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c5f3e83bbbd4aa501b5225ab6bb2b783a84040a3","tid":554794,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T02:13:35.000Z","msg":"聖約翰救傷隊&mdash;&gt;華佗救傷隊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"童軍係英國野，要滅團，成立共青團香港支部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b4cf85196b51d15709fa48cf5c0b9a223f6389","tid":554794,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a02a47e7b7cc7598cf085ade17cdc3a30c5372ce","tid":554794,"uid":4519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c5f3e83bbbd4aa501b5225ab6bb2b783a84040a3","tid":554794,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T02:13:35.000Z","msg":"聖約翰救傷隊&mdash;&gt;華佗救傷隊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"童軍係英國野，要滅團，成立共青團香港支部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"基督少年軍要改近平少年軍"},{"pid":"0135131377569d447ae27011c175a70efb5b902e","tid":554794,"uid":105366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:48:42.000Z","msg":"士進制同一夫一妻制都係英式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabf4ba54c97bb3ccff94aefca602aa26e9628e6","tid":554794,"uid":19275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:58:29.000Z","msg":"啲留言好穩定地1個負評 邊隻五毛入左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053cb288a6350e9016c862956834380a7f4ad882","tid":554794,"uid":34852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eabf4ba54c97bb3ccff94aefca602aa26e9628e6","tid":554794,"uid":19275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:58:29.000Z","msg":"啲留言好穩定地1個負評 邊隻五毛入左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}